provenance.note:
Purchased from Blake by John Linnell, with *America* Copy O, for £1 on 8 August 1821; 
at Linnell's death in 1882 the book became the property of the Linnell Trust; sold by the Linnell Trustees at Christie's, 
15 March 1918, lot 172, with *America* Copy O (£787.10s. to the Carfax Gallery acting to T. H. Riches); 
bequeathed by Riches to the Fitzwilliam Museum in 1935 and received by the Fitzwilliam in 1950.
